    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国濒临毁灭。厄运的低语在街头回响，但无人知晓真相。城堡之下，早被遗忘的深渊中，有什么正在苏醒。那被封印的远古黑暗再次觉醒——而你，是唯一能揭示其秘密之人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Rune Ark</strong>中，<strong>三消战斗</strong>与地下城RPG完美融合。你扮演一位年轻侍从，原本只想证明自己，却意外发现禁忌之物，踏上为生存与王国命运而战的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/b561b05e0e361bf6ad15241b0f535ba1.poster.avif?t=1763485149\" width=778 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/b561b05e0e361bf6ad15241b0f535ba1.webm?t=1763485149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/b561b05e0e361bf6ad15241b0f535ba1.mp4?t=1763485149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次深入深渊，都会遇到新危险与被遗忘的真相。每场战斗都是技巧与意志的考验。<strong>消除方块释放古老力量，解开隐藏谜团，在变化莫测的深渊中前行</strong>。程序生成的地牢不仅藏有敌人，还有抉择。你的选择将影响剧情、结盟、敌对与多重结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你能在黑暗吞噬之前揭开Rune Ark的真相吗？你会成为英雄，还是被遗忘的灵魂？</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><br><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三消战斗：</strong> 通过解谜进行攻击、防御并释放强大技能。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情驱动RPG：</strong> 你的选择决定王国命运，带来多种结局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随机生成地牢：</strong> 每次探索都有新挑战、敌人与战利品，耐玩性高。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略成长系统：</strong> 提升技能、打造装备、结盟求生。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/2488e95d336ab6ef6583182de0705e47.poster.avif?t=1763485149\" width=778 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/2488e95d336ab6ef6583182de0705e47.webm?t=1763485149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/2488e95d336ab6ef6583182de0705e47.mp4?t=1763485149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>互动式叙事：</strong> 通过视觉小说式对话与角色互动影响世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗奇幻氛围：</strong> 手绘场景与沉浸式音乐展现神秘王国。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/1585085e192bfe8f9935ca69d6058785.poster.avif?t=1763485149\" width=778 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/1585085e192bfe8f9935ca69d6058785.webm?t=1763485149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128940/extras/1585085e192bfe8f9935ca69d6058785.mp4?t=1763485149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好准备——<i>Rune Ark</i>不仅仅是消除游戏，更是策略、坚韧与抉择的试炼。</p><br>",
